sudo apt install tshark -y 

**start capturing packets:
tshark -w tshark.pcap

**
wget https://github.com/gcla/termshark/releases/tag/v1.0.0/termshark_1.0.0_linux_x64.tar.gz
tar -xf termshark_1.0.0_linux_x64.tar.gz
cd termshark_1.0.0_linux_x64
cp termshark /usr/local/bin

***to monitor the captured packets:
termshark -r tshark.pcap
